UID:Ew3nQUl441W4YKngHGlG1
SUMMARY:The Films of Roy Fridge
DTSTAMP:20260623T103850Z
DTSTART:20260516T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:A program of rarely-seen experimental films made by Texas artis
	t Roy Fridge between the late-1950s and early-1970s\, introduced by his fr
	iend and gallerist Betty Moody. The program also includes a number of his 
