SUMMARY:Essays on Industrial Organization and Consumer Behavior
DTSTAMP:20260623T103851Z
DTSTART:20260710T150000Z
DESCRIPTION:&#160\;  Speaker: Ruosi Li  Doctoral Candidate  Thesis Defense 
	 Department: Economics  Location: Kraft Hall Kraft 402\; Zoom link: https:
	//riceuniversity.zoom.us/j/2460173918?pwd=d1p1NjN0ekwvclVXdkgybUQ0VXcxdz09
	&amp\;omn=94398956547  My dissertation contains two chapters\, and they ar
	e all about consumer demand estimation when consumers do not have a perfec
	t understanding of the products they are buying. The first chapter is abou
	t consumer confusion\, and the second one is about limited consideration. 
	 &#160\;  (Department : Economics)\n\nhttps://events.rice.edu/live/events/
	432734-essays-on-industrial-organization-and-consumer\n\nFrom Rice Univers
