SUMMARY:Rice University Summer Engineering Innovation Program - Demo Day 20
	26
DTSTAMP:20260623T103851Z
DTSTART:20260730T230000Z
DESCRIPTION:About the Summer Engineering Innovation Program at Rice Univers
	ityRice University's Summer Engineering Innovation Program (http://www.rce
	lconnect.org/seip) is a dynamic\, hands-on experience for students to solv
	e real-world challenges using Artificial Intelligence\, Digital Engineerin
	g\, Model-Based Systems Engineering (MBSE)\, and Industry 4.0 technologies
	. Over 10 weeks\, students will collaborate with industry leaders\, sharpe
	n technical skills\, and bring breakthrough ideas to life through project-
	based learning and mentorship.  Whether developing cutting-edge prototypes
	 or designing smart systems\, this program empowers students to turn theor
	y into impact.\n\nhttps://events.rice.edu/live/events/430602-rice-universi
	ty-summer-engineering-innovation\n\nFrom Rice University - Open to the Pub
	lic
URL:https://events.rice.edu/live/events/430602-rice-university-summer-engin
	eering-innovation
